[3] First deploy → 2 live bugs caught:
    BUG 1: loadConnectedAccountByToolkit queried `cloud_agents.settings` —
           the column is actually `composio_user_id`. Fixed inline.
    BUG 2: Initial ComposioClient.createTrigger hit `POST /api/v3.1/triggers`
           and got a 404 (the page was Composio's frontend Next.js 404 —
           wrong namespace + wrong path). Discovered via GitHub search
           of Composio's TS SDK source: actual endpoints are
             POST   /api/v3/trigger_instances/{slug}/upsert
             DELETE /api/v3/trigger_instances/manage/{triggerId}
           Body uses `connected_account_id` + optional `trigger_config`.
           Updated createTrigger to swap the v3.1 base to v3 just for
           the trigger endpoints. Documented inline.
    BUG 3: First schedule submission rejected with
           "Invalid Schedule Expression cron(0 9 * * MON-FRI)" —
           EventBridge requires 6-field cron with `?` in dom when dow is
           set. Added toEventBridgeCron() helper converting 5→6 fields:
             0 9 * * MON-FRI  →  0 9 ? * MON-FRI *

